long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Jelly Match 3 is a puzzle game where you match jellies to clear the board and score points. Play on any device. Give it a try!
Jelly Match 3 is a fun and addictive HTML5 puzzle game that will keep you entertained for hours. The game's goal is to check three or more jellies of the exact color to clear them from the board and score points.
To play the game, follow these steps:
	1	Use your mouse to click and drag jellies to make matches of three or more.
	2	Try making as many matches as possible before the time runs out.
	3	Use unique jellies like bombs and rainbow jellies to clear larger groups of jellies and earn more points.
	4	As you progress through the levels, the game will get more challenging, so stay focused and use your skills to get the highest score possible!
In addition to its engaging gameplay. And a catchy soundtrack that will keep you entertained. The game is optimized for all web browsers.
Jelly Match 3 is a must-play game for fans of puzzle games. Is anyone looking for a fun and thorny way to pass the time? Head over to the Jelly Match 3 website and start playing today!
